OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,FA coroner said he was "perplexed" by
OL,8,Fthe absence of representatives from
OL,9,Fthe Foreign Office at a hearing for a
OL,10,Fbackpacker from Kent who died after
OL,11,Fallegedly being served drinks laced
OL,12,Fwith methanol in Laos.
OL,14,FSimone White, 28, from Orpington, was
OL,15,Fone of a number of people taken to
OL,16,Fhospital when she had been staying in
OL,17,Fthe popular backpacking town of Vang
OL,18,FVieng.
OL,20,FShe died in hospital in Thailand on
OL,21,FNovember 21 2024.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@aO]
