PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772791513
OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,FAssistant coroner for South London
OL,8,FSebastian Naughton said he had invited
OL,9,Fa representative from the Foreign,
OL,10,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,11,F(FCDO) to attend the pre-inquest
OL,12,Freview hearing for Ms White on
OL,13,FThursday.
OL,15,F"I'm slightly perplexed by the absence
OL,16,Fof the Foreign Office representative,"
OL,17,FMr Naughton told South London
OL,18,FCoroners' Court, sitting at Croydon
OL,19,FTown Hall.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
