OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772791513
OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,FMs White's stepfather Neil White
OL,8,Fattended the hearing by video link and
OL,9,Fsaid he had received an update from
OL,10,Fthe FCDO regarding criminal
OL,11,Fproceedings in Laos.
OL,13,FFive other people died after consuming
OL,14,Ffree drinks served at the Nana
OL,15,FBackpacker Hostel, including two
OL,16,FAustralian teenagers, an American and
OL,17,Ftwo Danish tourists.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
