PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772791513
OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,F"The 10 (people) that were under
OL,8,Finvestigation (for destroying
OL,9,Fevidence) appeared in court and got
OL,10,Ffines of something like 120 dollars, I
OL,11,Fthink it was, in relation to I believe
OL,12,Fa US gentleman that passed away," Mr
OL,13,FWhite told the hearing.
OL,15,F"The distillery owner's investigation
OL,16,Ffor contamination is still ongoing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@aO]wD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
