PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772791513
OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,FMr White said his wife had travelled
OL,8,Fto south-east Asia when Ms White, a
OL,9,Flawyer, was in hospital and received
OL,10,Fdozens of pages of medical records
OL,11,Fthen.
OL,13,FHe stressed that he and his wife would
OL,14,Flike the inquest to proceed as quickly
OL,15,Fas possible, adding: "I don't think we
OL,16,Fare going to get anything meaningful
OL,17,Ffrom Laos."
OL,26,@wD@VOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
