OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772791513
OL,3,CCoroner 'perplexed' as Foreign Office
OL,4,Cfails to go to hearing for Kent
OL,5,Cbackpacker
OL,7,FThe coroner asked that Mr White
OL,8,Fprovide the medical records from the
OL,9,FThai hospital and asked Mr Duke to
OL,10,Fsupply the police interviews with Ms
OL,11,FWhite's travel companions for his
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FMr Naughton said a further pre-inquest
OL,15,Freview would be listed for April or
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FITV Meridian has contacted the Foreign
OL,19,FOffice for a response.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
